{"data":[{"date":"19:22 22/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 22/8: Martial ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u1edf MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-228-martial-ra-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai-o-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 22/8.</h2><h2>Marseille kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu Yaya Toure</h2>\r\n<div>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Marseille l\u00e0 Jacques-Henri Eyraud cho bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Velodrome kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Yaya Toure. C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man City hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ef1 do sau khi chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester h\u00e8 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Marseille kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Toure \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf cho Zambo-Anguissa m\u1edbi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Fulham.</div>\r\n<h2>Draxler c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn La Liga</h2>\r\n<div>Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Sevilla \u0111ang mong mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Draxler c\u1ee7a PSG. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed l\u00fac n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Wissam Ben Yedder s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Marseille ngay sau \u0111\u00f3.</div>\r\n<h2>Martial quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 228 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 228 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/Duoc-BLD-ung-ho-Martial-quyet-tam-chung-to-minh-o-MU-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 22/8: Martial quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>T\u1edd The Sun \u0111\u01b0a tin ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Anthony Martial \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Man United ngay d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Mourinho. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 t\u1ea1i Nga v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf MU. Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n<h2>Kante s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div>T\u1edd Le10Sport kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 N&rsquo;golo Kante \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp theo. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i theo \u0111u\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 Real Madrid hay Paris Saint-Germain. Nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Kante \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Chelsea d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Maurizio Sarri.</div>\r\n<h2>Man City nh\u1eafm th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n kh\u1ee7ng thay th\u1ebf Bravo</h2>\r\n<div>K\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Premier League nh\u01b0ng Man City \u0111ang nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Keylor Navas t\u1eeb Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Claudio Bravo. Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Chile nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00f3t ch\u00e2n. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Man xanh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 Ederson. V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t HLV th\u00edch xoay tua nh\u01b0 Pep Guardiola, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn. V\u00e0 v\u00ec v\u1eady, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang mong mu\u1ed1n Man City c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Navas c\u00e0ng s\u1edbm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n<div>Bongda24h.vn (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2665","checkdouble":"195094"},{"date":"19:41 22/08","title":"Ronaldo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/22/ronaldo-tiet-lo-ly-do-dau-quan-cho-juventus.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Cristiano Ronaldo th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 m\u00e0 c\u00e1c C\u0110V Juventus d\u00e0nh cho anh sau pha \u201cng\u1ea3 b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e8n\u201d l\u1ecbch s\u1eed h\u1ed3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh \u0111\u01b0a anh t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh Turin.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eddi cho Real Madrid v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Juventus \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i t\u1ea1i Turin. Pha b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c C\u0110V c\u1ee7a Juventus c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady c\u1ed5 v\u0169 anh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u00e1c Juventini c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1edd r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd khi \u1ea5y l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh \u0111\u01b0a Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/ronaldo-tiet-lo-ly-do-dau-quan-cho-juventus.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c C\u0110V Juve l\u00e0 l\u00fd do anh \u0111\u1ebfn Turin</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cNh\u1eefng chi ti\u1ebft nh\u1ecf l\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u1eddng mang \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1edbn. Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a Juventus khi \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 chi ti\u1ebft \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh 100% th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 33 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a anh khi \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng t\u1ea1o ra ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c C\u0110V Real m\u00e0 anh ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng th\u1ea5y tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 bao gi\u1edd.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cB\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i cho \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Khi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u khen ng\u1ee3i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng, c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c qu\u00e1 s\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cN\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u1edfi v\u00ec t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc kh\u00f3 tin trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft Juventus trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Chievo tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Tuy v\u1eady, si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng n\u00e0o trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Juventus:<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/hang-loat-doi-bong-lon-nhan-don-dau-vu-pjanic-176-195028.html\">H\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2n \u0111au v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-khong-the-giup-juventus-tiep-tuc-thong-tri-nuoc-y-176-195019.html\">Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Juventus ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)\u00a0</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2664","checkdouble":"195095"},{"date":"21:25 22/08","title":"\"Justin Kluivert \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00fang khi t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/justin-kluivert-da-dung-khi-tu-choi-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n \u0110T Olympic Bahrain t\u1ecf ra \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 trong tay HLV Park Hang Seo.\r\n\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Bahrain ch\u1ec9 ra 3 ng\u00f4i sao nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 23/8, \u0110T Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i &lsquo;m\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t, m\u1ed9t c\u00f2n&rsquo; v\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1 v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n \u0110T Olympic Bahrain Ahmed Bin Isa Al Khalifa \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra am hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Van Quyet\" title=\"V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/truong-doan-bahrain-chi-ra-3-ngoi-sao-nguy-hiem-nhat-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 3 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n \u0110T Olympic Bahrain \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng Ahmed n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Zing.vn: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1edbi xem m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t kinh nghi\u1ec7m. \u0110i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 10 (V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft) ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 18 (H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng) v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 19 (Quang H\u1ea3i).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i h\u01a1i ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean v\u00ec sao h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng thua g\u00ec c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n hay H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. S\u1ed1 19 c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a qu\u00ean tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a Bahrain tr\u01b0\u1edbc U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, khi h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 U20 World Cup. &ldquo;&ldquo;U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu. H\u1ecd ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhanh r\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thua v\u00ec b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 ng\u00e0y mai s\u1ebd ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i. Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft ASIAD&rdquo;, v\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n&nbsp;29 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y chia s\u1ebb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1ecb n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Malaysia \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Ahmed Bin Isa kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: &ldquo;\u0110\u00e3 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out, b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 t\u1eebng th\u1eafng Olympic Malaysia&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich-168-195103.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich-168-195103.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain (19h30 ng\u00e0y 23/8): Vi\u1ebft ti\u1ebfp k\u1ef3 t\u00edch</span><br />\r\n19h30 t\u1ed1i nay, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra. V\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-malaysia-hy-vong-olympic-viet-nam-se-tien-xa-tai-asiad-2018-168-195102.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/11/22/bao-nuoc-ngoai-nhan-dinh-gi-ve-tran-viet-nam-vs-malaysia.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-malaysia-hy-vong-olympic-viet-nam-se-tien-xa-tai-asiad-2018-168-195102.html\">HLV Malaysia hy v\u1ecdng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn xa t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span><br />\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Olympic Malaysia Ong Kim Swee \u0111\u00e3 hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn xa t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-don-hung-tin-ve-nhan-su-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain-168-195101.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/olympic-viet-nam-don-hung-tin-ve-nhan-su-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-don-hung-tin-ve-nhan-su-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain-168-195101.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00f3n hung tin v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bahrain</span><br />\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Bahrain t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t tin kh\u00f4ng vui v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2663","checkdouble":"195096"},{"date":"21:48 22/08","title":"Pep Guardiola tri \u00e2n Kompany nh\u00e2n d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/14/pep-guardiola-khen-ngoi-kompany-het-loi.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Pep Guardiola cho r\u1eb1ng Vincent Kompany l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong ng\u00e0y ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m 10 n\u0103m \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n t\u1edbi Etihad.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kompany gia nh\u1eadp Man City t\u1eeb Hamburg v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 22/8/2008 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng 7.65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, Kompany \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester gi\u00e0nh 3 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League, 3 League Cup, 1 FA Cup v\u00e0 2 Community Shield.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao 32 tu\u1ed5i g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Pep Guardiola v\u00ec nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Anh ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 28 l\u1ea7n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pep Guardiola tri \u00e2n Kompany nh\u00e2n d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Pep Guardiola tri \u00e2n Kompany nh\u00e2n d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/pep-guardiola-khen-ngoi-kompany-het-loi.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Pep Guardiola tri \u00e2n Kompany</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Guardiola v\u1eabn l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tri \u00e2n nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh t\u1ef1u c\u1ee7a Kompany trong v\u00f2ng 1 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 qua v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cKhi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi 10 n\u0103m th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u1edfi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. V\u1eady n\u00ean t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Kompany trong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e3 qua. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc sang n\u0103m th\u1ee9 3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng nhau. C\u1ea3m \u01a1n c\u1eadu r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, Vincent\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Kompany c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u00fac m\u1eebng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 trong d\u1ecbp k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb n\u00e0y. Bravo cho bi\u1ebft: <em>\u201cR\u1ea5t \u00edt c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 vinh d\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p nh\u01b0 Kompany v\u1edbi Man City\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Benjamin Mendy c\u0169ng vui m\u1eebng chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean Twitter: <em>\u201cAnh \u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sinh ra \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi CLB n\u00e0y. Anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng t\u1ed1t, m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man City:<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-muon-mua-keylor-navas-172-195072.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng, Man City g\u00f5 c\u1eeda Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-tinh-goi-lai-aro-muric-172-195048.html\">Kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, Man City gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft ra sao?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2662","checkdouble":"195097"},{"date":"22:24 22/08","title":"\"Modric ho\u1eb7c Kante x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng 2018\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/modric-hoac-kante-xung-dang-gianh-qua-bong-vang-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Jermain Jenas cho r\u1eb1ng danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t thi\u1ebfu c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi \u00edt b\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 Modric hay Kante.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 Lionel Messi \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb danh hi\u1ec7u C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. Kaka l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh hi\u1ec7u Ballon d\u2019Or ngo\u00e0i Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1edd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a CLB. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Jenas tin r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u1edf World Cup nh\u01b0ng ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n c\u0169ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 tr\u1ecdng v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Modric ho\u1eb7c Kante x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Modric ho\u1eb7c Kante x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/modric-hoac-kante-xung-dang-gianh-qua-bong-vang-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jenas cho r\u1eb1ng Modric x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf m\u1ecdi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh cho danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ch\u00fang ta \u0111ang \u1edf trong m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean thi\u1ebfu \u0111i s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cNh\u1eefng g\u00ec Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n r\u1eb1ng ai trong hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng. Khi b\u1ea1n th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u01b0 Iniesta hay Xavi ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd gi\u00e0nh Ballon d\u2019Or th\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1eb1ng ch\u1eb3ng ai gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00f3 ngo\u00e0i Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi.<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cC\u1ea3 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngo\u00e0i h\u00e0nh tinh. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 Modric m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Ribery c\u1ee7a Bayern\u00a0 v\u00e0i n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, b\u1ea1n th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e9t \u0111\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cGi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y Kante c\u0169ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u00e0o h\u00e0ng ng\u0169 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u00f9 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi nh\u1eadn nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ghi nh\u1eadn t\u1eeb gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng Ballon d\u2019Or. K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 sau khi gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t c\u0169ng l\u00e0 Pogba v\u00ec s\u1ef1 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u kh\u00e1c:<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-tiet-lo-ly-do-dau-quan-cho-juventus-176-195095.html\">Ronaldo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-228-martial-ra-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai-o-mu-184-195094.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 22/8: Martial ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u1edf MU</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2661","checkdouble":"195098"},{"date":"05:39 23/08","title":"Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Bahrain ch\u1ec9 ra 3 ng\u00f4i sao nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/truong-doan-bahrain-chi-ra-3-ngoi-sao-nguy-hiem-nhat-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n \u0110T Olympic Bahrain t\u1ecf ra \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 trong tay HLV Park Hang Seo.\r\n\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Bahrain ch\u1ec9 ra 3 ng\u00f4i sao nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 23/8, \u0110T Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i &lsquo;m\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t, m\u1ed9t c\u00f2n&rsquo; v\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1 v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n \u0110T Olympic Bahrain Ahmed Bin Isa Al Khalifa \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra am hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Van Quyet\" title=\"V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/truong-doan-bahrain-chi-ra-3-ngoi-sao-nguy-hiem-nhat-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 3 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n \u0110T Olympic Bahrain \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng Ahmed n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Zing.vn: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1edbi xem m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t kinh nghi\u1ec7m. \u0110i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 10 (V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft) ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 18 (H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng) v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 19 (Quang H\u1ea3i).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i h\u01a1i ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean v\u00ec sao h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng thua g\u00ec c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n hay H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. S\u1ed1 19 c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a qu\u00ean tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a Bahrain tr\u01b0\u1edbc U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, khi h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 U20 World Cup. &ldquo;&ldquo;U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu. H\u1ecd ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhanh r\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thua v\u00ec b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 ng\u00e0y mai s\u1ebd ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i. Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft ASIAD&rdquo;, v\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n&nbsp;29 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y chia s\u1ebb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1ecb n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Malaysia \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Ahmed Bin Isa kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: &ldquo;\u0110\u00e3 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out, b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 t\u1eebng th\u1eafng Olympic Malaysia&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich-168-195103.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich-168-195103.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain (19h30 ng\u00e0y 23/8): Vi\u1ebft ti\u1ebfp k\u1ef3 t\u00edch</span><br />\r\n19h30 t\u1ed1i nay, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra. V\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-malaysia-hy-vong-olympic-viet-nam-se-tien-xa-tai-asiad-2018-168-195102.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/11/22/bao-nuoc-ngoai-nhan-dinh-gi-ve-tran-viet-nam-vs-malaysia.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-malaysia-hy-vong-olympic-viet-nam-se-tien-xa-tai-asiad-2018-168-195102.html\">HLV Malaysia hy v\u1ecdng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn xa t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span><br />\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Olympic Malaysia Ong Kim Swee \u0111\u00e3 hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn xa t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-don-hung-tin-ve-nhan-su-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain-168-195101.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/olympic-viet-nam-don-hung-tin-ve-nhan-su-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-don-hung-tin-ve-nhan-su-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain-168-195101.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00f3n hung tin v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bahrain</span><br />\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Bahrain t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t tin kh\u00f4ng vui v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2660","checkdouble":"195099"},{"date":"05:54 23/08","title":"Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen c\u00f3 l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Th\u00e1i Lan","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/viet-nam-duoc-khen-co-lua-cau-thu-tre-tot-hon-thai-lan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, c\u00e2y b\u00fat c\u1ee7a t\u1edd Fox Sports Asia \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.\r\n\r\n</h2><br>\r\n<h2>Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen c\u00f3 l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Th\u00e1i Lan<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Park Hang Seo. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng vang d\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 m\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo c\u0169ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft ASIAD, \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 ch\u00fang ta ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen c\u00f3 l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Th\u00e1i Lan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen c\u00f3 l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Th\u00e1i Lan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/Viet-Nam-duoc-khen-co-lua-cau-thu-tre-tot-hon-Thai-Lan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen c\u00f3 l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Th\u00e1i Lan</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u00e2y b\u00fat Scott McIntyre c\u1ee7a&nbsp;Fox Sports Asia&nbsp;chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi Zing.vn: &quot;M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng khen ng\u1ee3i. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Park qu\u00e1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u00fang l\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00ean h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi. T\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng di chuy\u1ec3n \u00e1p s\u00e1t v\u00e0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 pressing g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p..., c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb \u01b0u t\u00fa h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Th\u00e1i Lan, n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi nay. B\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng l\u00e0 sau th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a &ldquo;Messi Th\u00e1i&rdquo; Chanathip, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a &ldquo;nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa voi Th\u00e1i&rdquo; \u0111ang th\u1ee5t l\u00f9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u1edf c\u1ea3 gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 l\u1eabn ASIAD, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 4 n\u0103m v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u00fd ki\u1ebfn cho r\u1eb1ng Th\u00e1i Lan kh\u00f4ng g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn ASIAD 2018 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t, tuy nhi\u00ean Scott McIntyre kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh quan \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. \u00d4ng ph\u00e2n t\u00edch m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eaft, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng Scott McIntyre c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p Bahrain v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay. Nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Australia cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 c\u1ee9 h\u00e3y v\u1eefng tin v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00fang v\u1edbi n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u1ecb n\u00e0y cho r\u1eb1ng \u1edf c\u00e1c c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ebb, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n, v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean \u0111\u1eb7t n\u1eb7ng v\u00e0o k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich-168-195103.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich-168-195103.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain (19h30 ng\u00e0y 23/8): Vi\u1ebft ti\u1ebfp k\u1ef3 t\u00edch</span><br>\r\n19h30 t\u1ed1i nay, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra. V\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-dung-toan-tay-a-khi-tam-huy-chuong-dang-rat-gan-168-194952.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/HLV-Le-Thuy-Hai-du-doan-thanh-tich-cua-DT-Olympic-Viet-Nam-tai-AS-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-dung-toan-tay-a-khi-tam-huy-chuong-dang-rat-gan-168-194952.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee5ng to\u00e0n T\u00e2y \u00c1: Khi t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n</span><br>\r\n\u1ede m\u1ed9t nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p to\u00e0n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb T\u00e2y \u00c1, \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1m may cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u00ean con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chinh ph\u1ee5c t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&#10;\" times=\"\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2659","checkdouble":"195100"},{"date":"06:04 23/08","title":"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00f3n hung tin v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bahrain","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/olympic-viet-nam-don-hung-tin-ve-nhan-su-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Bahrain t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t tin kh\u00f4ng vui v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</h2><br>\r\n<h2>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00f3n hung tin v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bahrain <o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00f3n hung tin v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bahrain h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00f3n hung tin v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bahrain h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/c51123c0-11a0-4590-8f1b-b2644e50e1b4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bahrain&nbsp;</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u 22/8, m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi di\u1ec5n ra tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Bahrain, m\u1ed9t tin kh\u00f4ng vui \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi v\u1edbi HLV Park Hang Seo. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, trung v\u1ec7 ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp nh\u1eb9 d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u00e1c s\u0129. Theo chia s\u1ebb t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam cho bi\u1ebft, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ng\u00e0y mai v\u1edbi Bahrain hi\u1ec7n ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh. HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1ea7n th\u00eam \u00fd ki\u1ebfn b\u00e1c s\u0129 v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u, \u00f4ng Park s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean V\u0103n H\u1eadu v\u00e0 V\u0103n L\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1edfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC l\u00e0 ch\u1ed1t ch\u1eb7n quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u00e0 Duy M\u1ea1nh, c\u1ea3 ba gi\u00fap cho h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 U23 r\u1ed3i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 \u0103n \u00fd, s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh v\u1edbi nhau k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Trung Qu\u1ed1c. T\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD, h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 l\u00e0 tuy\u1ebfn ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, khi ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi b\u00e0n n\u00e0o. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh tr\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c v\u1eafng \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i to\u00e1n v\u1edbi HLV Park Hang Seo khi g\u1eb7p Bahrain v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich-168-195103.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich-168-195103.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain (19h30 ng\u00e0y 23/8): Vi\u1ebft ti\u1ebfp k\u1ef3 t\u00edch</span><br>\r\n19h30 t\u1ed1i nay, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra. V\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/viet-nam-duoc-khen-co-lua-cau-thu-tre-tot-hon-thai-lan-168-195100.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/viet-nam-duoc-khen-co-lua-cau-thu-tre-tot-hon-thai-lan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/viet-nam-duoc-khen-co-lua-cau-thu-tre-tot-hon-thai-lan-168-195100.html\">Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen c\u00f3 l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Th\u00e1i Lan</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, c\u00e2y b\u00fat c\u1ee7a t\u1edd Fox Sports Asia \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-bahrain-chi-ra-3-ngoi-sao-nguy-hiem-nhat-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-195099.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/truong-doan-bahrain-chi-ra-3-ngoi-sao-nguy-hiem-nhat-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-bahrain-chi-ra-3-ngoi-sao-nguy-hiem-nhat-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-195099.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Bahrain ch\u1ec9 ra 3 ng\u00f4i sao nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTrao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n \u0110T Olympic Bahrain t\u1ecf ra \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 trong tay HLV Park Hang Seo.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-dung-toan-tay-a-khi-tam-huy-chuong-dang-rat-gan-168-194952.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/HLV-Le-Thuy-Hai-du-doan-thanh-tich-cua-DT-Olympic-Viet-Nam-tai-AS-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-dung-toan-tay-a-khi-tam-huy-chuong-dang-rat-gan-168-194952.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee5ng to\u00e0n T\u00e2y \u00c1: Khi t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n</span><br>\r\n\u1ede m\u1ed9t nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p to\u00e0n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb T\u00e2y \u00c1, \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1m may cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u00ean con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chinh ph\u1ee5c t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2658","checkdouble":"195101"},{"date":"06:17 23/08","title":"HLV Malaysia hy v\u1ecdng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn xa t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/11/22/bao-nuoc-ngoai-nhan-dinh-gi-ve-tran-viet-nam-vs-malaysia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Olympic Malaysia Ong Kim Swee \u0111\u00e3 hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn xa t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.\r\n\r\n</h2><br>\r\n<h2>HLV Malaysia hy v\u1ecdng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn xa t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i trong s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Malaysia l\u00e0 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u00e2u \u0111\u1eadm nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ea1 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng th\u00ec Malaysia th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd cho t\u1ea5m HCV ASIAD, \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Malaysia hy v\u1ecdng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn xa t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Malaysia hy v\u1ecdng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn xa t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/HLV-Malaysia-hy-vong-Olympic-Viet-Nam-se-tien-xa-tai-ASIAD-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV&nbsp;Ong Kim Swee k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ea3 Malaysia v\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh s\u1ef1 th\u0103ng hoa c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 trong n\u0103m nay l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn HLV Ong Kim Swee tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 khu v\u1ef1c t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ASIAD.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Malaysia \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i ch\u00e2u \u00c1. V\u1edbi l\u1ee9a tu\u1ed5i U23, ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u1edf t\u1ea7m ch\u00e2u \u00c1 th\u00ec ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 m\u00e0 v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1ea7m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5y r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea5y, Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf l\u1ee9a U23 v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 \u0110TQG n\u1eefa. \u1ede Malaysia ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0m nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Hi v\u1ecdng nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf l\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp n\u1ed1i \u1edf \u0110TQG trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai kh\u00f4ng xa&rdquo;, HLV Ong Kim Swee cho hay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 47 tu\u1ed5i&nbsp;c\u00f2n n\u00f3i th\u00eam: &quot;C\u00f3 ai ngh\u0129 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eafng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n? \u0110\u00f3 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 v\u1eady. Nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 l\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ea5y th\u00f4i. Quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i d\u00e1m \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Malaysia v\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh ti\u1ebfn b\u01b0\u1edbc, m\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Bahrain trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Malaysia s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt. N\u1ebfu thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00fang s\u1ee9c, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich-168-195103.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich-168-195103.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain (19h30 ng\u00e0y 23/8): Vi\u1ebft ti\u1ebfp k\u1ef3 t\u00edch</span><br>\r\n19h30 t\u1ed1i nay, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra. V\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/viet-nam-duoc-khen-co-lua-cau-thu-tre-tot-hon-thai-lan-168-195100.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/viet-nam-duoc-khen-co-lua-cau-thu-tre-tot-hon-thai-lan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/viet-nam-duoc-khen-co-lua-cau-thu-tre-tot-hon-thai-lan-168-195100.html\">Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen c\u00f3 l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Th\u00e1i Lan</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, c\u00e2y b\u00fat c\u1ee7a t\u1edd Fox Sports Asia \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-don-hung-tin-ve-nhan-su-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain-168-195101.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/olympic-viet-nam-don-hung-tin-ve-nhan-su-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-don-hung-tin-ve-nhan-su-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain-168-195101.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00f3n hung tin v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bahrain</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Bahrain t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t tin kh\u00f4ng vui v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-bahrain-chi-ra-3-ngoi-sao-nguy-hiem-nhat-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-195099.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/truong-doan-bahrain-chi-ra-3-ngoi-sao-nguy-hiem-nhat-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-bahrain-chi-ra-3-ngoi-sao-nguy-hiem-nhat-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-195099.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Bahrain ch\u1ec9 ra 3 ng\u00f4i sao nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTrao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n \u0110T Olympic Bahrain t\u1ecf ra \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 trong tay HLV Park Hang Seo.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2657","checkdouble":"195102"},{"date":"06:55 23/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain (19h30 ng\u00e0y 23/8): Vi\u1ebft ti\u1ebfp k\u1ef3 t\u00edch","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/23/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>19h30 t\u1ed1i nay, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra. V\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf.</h2><h2>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ebfp n\u1ed1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Th\u01b0\u1eddng Ch\u00e2u t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111ang ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh vi\u1ebft n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch khi \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft ASIAD 2018. N\u1ebfu gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng 8 \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 thao ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain (19h30 ng\u00e0y 238)  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain (19h30 ng\u00e0y 238)  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>&nbsp;Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain:&nbsp;Vi\u1ebft ti\u1ebfp k\u1ef3 t\u00edch</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n, tr\u00ean con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 to\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi b\u00e0n n\u00e0o. \u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch &lsquo;v\u00f4 ti\u1ec1n kho\u1eafng h\u1eadu&rsquo; trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u00eam Uzbekistan l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c ch\u00e0ng trai \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf d\u0129 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn c\u1eeda tr\u00ean t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 b\u1edfi l\u00fac n\u00e0y, l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng l\u00e0m n\u00ean t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, \u1edf gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng 3 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t d\u00e0y d\u1ea1n kinh nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e0 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft. Ch\u00ednh s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng d\u00f9 trong 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi 3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c nhau. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch gi\u1eefa \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. V\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Olympic Bahrain ch\u1ec9 mang \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U21 d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i, ch\u00fang ta ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00fang s\u1ee9c v\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-khi-asiad-bay-gio-moi-thuc-su-bat-dau-168-194951.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-khi-asiad-bay-gio-moi-thuc-su-bat-dau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-khi-asiad-bay-gio-moi-thuc-su-bat-dau-168-194951.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain: Khi ASIAD b\u00e2y gi\u1edd m\u1edbi th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u</span><br>\r\nOlympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Song tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bahrain s\u1eafp t\u1edbi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo b\u1edfi s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Olympic Bahrain &ndash; tr\u1ebb, kh\u1ecfe nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 non kinh nghi\u1ec7m?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ec9 mang theo m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh g\u1ed3m l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111a ph\u1ea7n ch\u1ec9 21 tu\u1ed5i gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, \u0110T Olympic Bahrain kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh \u1edf ASIAD n\u0103m nay. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">So v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u1ee7a Bahrain tr\u1eafc tr\u1edf h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, h\u1ecd m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i U23 Malaysia \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c (s\u1edbm gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9). Ch\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 ho\u00e0i nghi c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Samir Chammam s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 binh h\u00f9ng, t\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1ea1nh \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Bahrain\" title=\"Olympic Bahrain\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/doi-truong-olympic-bahrain-ke-thach-thuc-giac-mo-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Olympic Bahrain mang \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ASIAD tr\u1ebb h\u01a1n Vi\u1ec7t Nam&nbsp;</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Bahrain v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb, kh\u00e1t khao chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. D\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 20, 21 song c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Bahrain c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh, chi\u1ec1u cao r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn hay tranh ch\u1ea5p tay \u0111\u00f4i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabu sao l\u00fac n\u00e0y, Olympic Bahrain v\u1eabn \u0111ang thua k\u00e9m Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1ec1 kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9 qu\u00e1i trong thi \u0111\u1ea5u. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. H\u01a1n h\u1ebft, \u0111\u1ee9ng sau l\u01b0ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t Park Hang Seo d\u1ea1n d\u00e0y kinh nghi\u1ec7m tr\u1eadn m\u1ea1c. V\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n s\u1ebd bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">8 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Olympic Bahrain v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-1 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2010, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2016, Quang H\u1ea3i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169ng t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng trang l\u1ee9a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bahrain t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng c\u00e1i duy\u00ean chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bahrain s\u1ebd gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 8 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c1.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7t Nam: Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng; \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng, Duy M\u1ea1nh, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, V\u0103n H\u1eadu, V\u0103n Thanh, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Quang H\u1ea3i, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bahrain: Ahmed; Bughammar, Alshamsan, Yahya Ali, Marhoon, Sanad, Hardan, Alsalama, Alkarrani, Hashim, Ahmedi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3&nbsp;Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain: 2-0</p>\r\n<h3>Highlight Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (ASIAD 2018)</h3>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/19/180014-Highlight-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Nhat-Ban-full.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-malaysia-hy-vong-olympic-viet-nam-se-tien-xa-tai-asiad-2018-168-195102.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/11/22/bao-nuoc-ngoai-nhan-dinh-gi-ve-tran-viet-nam-vs-malaysia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-malaysia-hy-vong-olympic-viet-nam-se-tien-xa-tai-asiad-2018-168-195102.html\">HLV Malaysia hy v\u1ecdng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn xa t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Olympic Malaysia Ong Kim Swee \u0111\u00e3 hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn xa t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-don-hung-tin-ve-nhan-su-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain-168-195101.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/olympic-viet-nam-don-hung-tin-ve-nhan-su-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-don-hung-tin-ve-nhan-su-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain-168-195101.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00f3n hung tin v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bahrain</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Bahrain t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t tin kh\u00f4ng vui v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-bahrain-chi-ra-3-ngoi-sao-nguy-hiem-nhat-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-195099.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/truong-doan-bahrain-chi-ra-3-ngoi-sao-nguy-hiem-nhat-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-bahrain-chi-ra-3-ngoi-sao-nguy-hiem-nhat-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-195099.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Bahrain ch\u1ec9 ra 3 ng\u00f4i sao nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTrao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n \u0110T Olympic Bahrain t\u1ecf ra \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 trong tay HLV Park Hang Seo.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ea1nh C\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2656","checkdouble":"195103"},{"date":"15:21 22/08","title":"Manchester \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t Arsenal-Wenger th\u1ee9 hai","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/manchester-dang-tro-thanh-mot-arsenalwenger-thu-hai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Ian Wright bi quan nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf th\u00e0nh Manchester \u0111ang d\u1ea7n sa l\u1ea7y v\u00e0o c\u01a1n kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng kh\u00f4ng l\u1ed1i tho\u00e1t nh\u01b0 Arsenal nh\u1eefng n\u0103m cu\u1ed1i tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Arsene Wenger.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Manchester United d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Jose Mourinho, c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha th\u00eam ph\u1ea7n lung lay d\u1eef d\u1ed9i, d\u1ef1 c\u1ea3m \u0111i\u1ec1m b\u00e1o kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0nh v\u1ec1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2015-16 c\u1ee7a Chelsea khi \u00f4ng b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Gi\u00e1ng Sinh.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh Arsenal th\u1eddi Wenger h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh Arsenal th\u1eddi Wenger h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/man-utd-gio-chang-khac-nao-tro-he-cho-thien-ha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ian Wright th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n li\u00ean t\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ebfn Arsenal nh\u1eefng n\u0103m cu\u1ed1i t\u00e0n d\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Arsene Wenger. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o Th\u1ee7 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i: \u201c\u0110\u00e1ng bu\u1ed3n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Man Utd hi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd l\u00e0 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee9u ch\u1eefa v\u1edbi Mourinho r\u1ed3i, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p t\u00f4i c\u00f3 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e0o.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 h\u1ed9i ch\u1ee9ng n\u0103m th\u1ee9 ba c\u1ee7a Mourinho v\u00e0 nghe c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u00ecn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u00f4ng \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ra m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n, c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 ch\u00ednh \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn r\u1ed3i. Theo nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c nhau, Man Utd giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0y \u0111ang bi\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t Arsenal th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 cu\u1ed1i tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Arsene Wenger, ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00f4 v\u1ecdng.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Mourinho \u0111ang m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn s\u00e2u s\u1eafc v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o va c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man Utd, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Tottenham s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Old Trafford v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh gi\u1ecdt n\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u00e0n ly.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-vs-man-city-172-194853.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/mourinho-cay-dang-chia-se-ve-tran-thua-tham-o-brighton.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-vs-man-city-172-194853.html\">Man Utd thua th\u1ea3m: \u0110\u00fang r\u1ed3i Jose, ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p!</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton cho th\u1ea5y Jose Mourinho gi\u1edd \u1edf v\u1ecb th\u1ebf m\u00e0 l\u1eddi m\u1ec9a mai Man City nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho Pep Guardiola ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p n\u1eefa r\u1ed3i,...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-vs-man-city-172-194855.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/Du-am-Brighton-vs-MU-Dung-roi-Jose,-tien-khong-the-mua-dang-cap-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-vs-man-city-172-194855.html\">M.U phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Jose Mourinho: Con thuy\u1ec1n m\u1ea5t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u01b0\u1edbng</span><br>\r\nN\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1m \u0111\u00e1y c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c C\u0110V Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf t\u1ed9i nghi\u1ec7p cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1eabn b\u1ecb k\u00e9o xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton. L\u1eddi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2655","checkdouble":"195074"},{"date":"15:22 22/08","title":"Tay \u0111ua Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Th\u1eadt th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/22/tay-dua-nguyen-thi-that-that-bai-o-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh HC v\u00e0ng nh\u01b0ng V\u0110V qu\u00ea An Giang ch\u1ec9 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch th\u1ee9 5 \u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111ua 104 km t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Tr\u01b0a 22/8, Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Th\u1eadt b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1eddng 104 km c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u1eef \u1edf Asiad 2018. Tay \u0111ua qu\u00ea An Giang li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong nh\u00f3m d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u khi cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u00f4i v\u1ec1 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00f4 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ee9t l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng. Chung cu\u1ed9c, Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Th\u1eadt v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch th\u1ee9 5 v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch 2 gi\u1edd 57 ph\u00fat 35 gi\u00e2y.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tay \u0111ua Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Th\u1eadt th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tay \u0111ua Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Th\u1eadt th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/that1-6618-1534925342.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Th\u1eadt cho bi\u1ebft c\u00f4 \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u01b0a 22/8. \u1ea2nh: \u0110\u1ee9c \u0110\u1ed3ng.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u00e0nh HC v\u00e0ng l\u00e0 V\u0110V c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c Na Ahreum v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch 2 gi\u1edd 55 ph\u00fat 47 gi\u00e2y (nhanh h\u01a1n Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Th\u1eadt 1 ph\u00fat 48 gi\u00e2y). Tay \u0111ua ng\u01b0\u1eddi Trung Qu\u1ed1c Pu Yixian \u0111o\u1ea1t HC b\u1ea1c c\u00f2n HC \u0111\u1ed3ng thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 cua r\u01a1 Yonamine Eri c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua di\u1ec5n ra, Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Th\u1eadt l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n th\u1ec3 thao Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u 22/8. H\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 2 v\u1eeba qua, c\u00f4 t\u1eebng \u0111o\u1ea1t ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111ua xe \u0111\u1ea1p ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 t\u1ea1i Myanmar khi ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh l\u1ed9 tr\u00ecnh 106 km sau trong 3 gi\u1edd 11 ph\u00fat 59 gi\u00e2y. C\u00f2n \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i Asiad, tay \u0111ua ng\u01b0\u1eddi An Giang t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh HC b\u1ea1c c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\"T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng. Tay \u0111ua c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u00f4i t\u1eebng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00f4 \u1ea5y cao h\u01a1n t\u00f4i m\u1ed9t b\u1eadc. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 ch\u1ecbu \u00e1p l\u1ef1c n\u00e0o c\u1ea3. Xin c\u1ea3m \u01a1n m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 quan t\u00e2m v\u00e0 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 t\u00f4i\", Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Th\u1eadt chia s\u1ebb sau khi v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u1ede n\u1ed9i dung n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Th\u1eadt l\u00e0 Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Thi c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 11, ch\u1eadm h\u01a1n V\u0110V gi\u00e0nh HC v\u00e0ng Na Ahreum 2 ph\u00fat 53 gi\u00e2y.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTheo ngoisao.net<br />\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2654","checkdouble":"195075"},{"date":"16:06 22/08","title":"Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng HLV Klopp v\u1eabn \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n t\u1eeb Naby Keita","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/22/khoi-dau-an-tuong-hlv-klopp-van-doi-hoi-nhieu-hon-tu-naby-keita.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jack Wilshere ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 26 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f9ng West Ham gi\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB c\u0169 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng minh h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 sai khi \u0111\u1ea9y anh ra \u0111i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Wilshere ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi Arsenal</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Arsenal quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Jack Wilshere. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi m\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi t\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 v\u00e0 anh bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Emirates.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong v\u00e0i n\u0103m qua, Wilshere li\u00ean t\u1ee5c d\u00ednh nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng. Anh ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u0169ng theo \u0111\u00f3 \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jack Wilshere ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jack Wilshere ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/wilshere-phat-bieu-ve-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Jack Wilshere ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng minh h\u1ecd sai</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a HLV Arsene Wenger, Wilshere t\u1eebng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng Mikel Arteta s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Arsenal v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec Unai Emery m\u1edbi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn ng\u1ed3i gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 Wilshere ra \u0111i d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do. Kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau, anh k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi West Ham.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9ng minh Arsenal sai</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau 11 n\u0103m kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Arsenal, Jack Wilshere chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u CLB c\u0169 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y tr\u00ean ch\u00ednh s\u00e2n Emirates t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 3 Premier League. Nh\u00e2n d\u1ecbp n\u00e0y, Jack Wilshere ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal. Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i m\u00e1i nh\u00e0 x\u01b0a \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng minh h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 sai khi h\u1eaft h\u1ee7i m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cArsenal \u0111\u00e3 sai khi ru\u1ed3ng b\u1ecf t\u00f4i. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y\u201d, Wilshere n\u00f3i. \u201cS\u1eafp t\u1edbi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. T\u00f4i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ebfn Emirates v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Arsenal tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1ea1i Bolton hay Bournemouth.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nWest Ham \u0111ang kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u Premier League kh\u00e1 t\u1ec7 khi thua l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t 0-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool v\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bournemouth. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Wilshere t\u1ef1 tin h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i cho Arsenal, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Emery.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00f4i mong ch\u1edd\u201d, Wilshere n\u00f3i. \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00e1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a West Ham.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Arsenal tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/manchester-dang-tro-thanh-mot-arsenalwenger-thu-hai-172-195074.html\">Manchester \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t Arsenal-Wenger th\u1ee9 hai</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/neville-arsenal-khong-dang-nhan-nhung-chi-trich-172-195070.html\">Neville: Arsenal kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/emery-khong-ngai-tram-cong-than-arsenal-172-195069.html\">Emery kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i tr\u1ea3m c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-yeu-cau-arsenal-tuc-toc-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-ramsey-172-195042.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i gi\u1ee5c Arsenal t\u1ee9c t\u1ed1c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ramsey</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-van-chua-the-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-ramsey-vi-172-195040.html\">Arsenal v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ramsey v\u00ec...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ozil-dang-phai-chien-dau-cho-tuong-lai-o-arsenal-172-195031.html\">Ozil \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u1edf Arsenal</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2653","checkdouble":"195077"},{"date":"16:30 22/08","title":"Chelsea c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid v\u1ee5 Marcos Alonso","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/chelsea-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-2-doi-bong-thanh-madrid-vu-marcos-alonso.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea b\u00e1n Marcos Alonso l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 \u0111\u1ea1i gia La Liga quan t\u00e2m Alonso</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Marcos Alonso ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Chelsea, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ghi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf La Liga mu\u1ed1n Chelsea b\u00e1n Marcos Alonso h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf La Liga mu\u1ed1n Chelsea b\u00e1n Marcos Alonso h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/chelsea-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-2-doi-bong-thanh-madrid-vu-marcos-alonso.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Marcos Alonso ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/marcos-alonso-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-real-madrid-180-182943.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Marcos Alonso</span>, Atletico Madrid v\u00e0 Barca c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf La Liga ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro nh\u1eb1m thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Chelsea nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ngo\u00e0i ra h\u1ecd c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19, 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf La Liga hy v\u1ecdng nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u1edbn s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n. Tuy nhi\u00ean Chelsea \u0111ang t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Marcos Alonso</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea b\u00e1n Marcos Alonso l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea khong ban Marcos Alonso\" title=\"Chelsea kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Marcos Alonso\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/chelsea-khong-ban-marcos-alonso.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Marcos Alonso \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Sarri kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge, b\u1edfi v\u1eady nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ra \u0111i. Chelsea s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb d\u00e0nh cho Alonso.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Huddersfield 3-0 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch v\u00e0 h\u1ea1 Arsenal 3-2 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. \u1ede hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y Alonso \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Huddersfield, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i mang v\u1ec1 1 qu\u1ea3 11m, \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Arsenal anh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2652","checkdouble":"195078"},{"date":"16:14 22/08","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n t\u00e2ng b\u1ed1c Jorginho sau kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u trong m\u01a1 \u1edf Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/22/nguoi-dai-dien-tang-boc-jorginho-sau-khoi-dau-trong-mo-o-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Jorginho t\u1ea1i Chelsea kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean b\u1edfi \u201cc\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e2u\u201d.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Jorginho \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp kh\u00e1 nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1edbi. V\u00e0 s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri c\u00e0ng t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 cho tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Chelsea. V\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 Joao Santos kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd nghi ng\u1edd v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng t\u00e2ng b\u1ed1c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng t\u00e2ng b\u1ed1c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/nguoi-dai-dien-tang-boc-jorginho-sau-khoi-dau-trong-mo-cung-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n t\u00e2ng b\u1ed1c Jorginho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;Jorginho \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Chelsea r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 n\u00f3i ti\u1ebfng Anh r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. T\u00f4i th\u1ea5y Jorginho kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf Chelsea c\u1ea3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Khi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t th\u00ec c\u1eadu ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o. N\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u00ec h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e2u&rdquo;.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nJorginho \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Chelsea kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 v\u1edbi 2 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Premier League. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a The Blues l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal trong tr\u1eadn derby London.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;Jorginho r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Arsenal. C\u00f3 t\u1edbi 50 C\u0110V t\u1eeb Napoli \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi c\u1ed5 v\u0169 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 xin ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh sau tr\u1eadn. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao ch\u00fang t\u00f4i y\u00eau Naples v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u1eef t\u00ecnh y\u00eau n\u00e0y. S\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c d\u00f9 Jorginho \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi London&rdquo;.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Chelsea:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-2-doi-bong-thanh-madrid-vu-marcos-alonso-172-195078.html\">Chelsea c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid v\u1ee5 Marcos Alonso</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/lucas-piazon-sap-roi-chelsea-172-195071.html\">&ldquo;H\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i&rdquo; Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb sang Ligue 1</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2651","checkdouble":"195082"}]}